id=oneui_brightness_fix
name=OneUI ROM Brightness Fix
version=v3.0
versionCode=3
author=combeng6th
description=Fixes broken brightness and adaptive brightness on custom Samsung OneUI ROMs and kernels where the lights HAL doesn't match the hardware. Stops the broken HAL and replaces it with a native daemon that reads the ambient light sensor directly.
